13:45.296 --> 13:47.263
Yeah, not understanding me.
I got to go.

13:47.298 --> 13:49.133
I'm gonna look
into this Lexy person on my own.

13:49.168 --> 13:50.563
She was on the phone
with someone at the courthouse,

13:50.598 --> 13:52.466
and I don't know. Something.

13:52.501 --> 13:54.336
Thank you.
No.

13:54.371 --> 13:57.504
