We need to quickly pivot

15:30.038 --> 15:31.334
to a criminal defense.

15:31.369 --> 15:32.698
Can you please
sit down now?

15:32.733 --> 15:34.667
(sighs)
Thank you.

15:34.702 --> 15:37.505
May I ask you,
where was the mayor last night?

15:37.540 --> 15:39.144
And his wife?

15:39.179 --> 15:41.278
And you. Were you...?

15:41.313 --> 15:43.676
They're questioning the mayor
later today.

15:43.711 --> 15:47.020
And if this escalates,
there's a process

15:47.055 --> 15:49.319
for charging an elected official
with a crime.

15:49.354 --> 15:51.552
Uh, Margaret, will you get

15:51.587 --> 15:53.554
volume 19 of the Oregon

15:53.589 --> 15:55.523
Penal Code from the credenza?

15:55.558 --> 16:00.396
It's, uh, volume 14.

16:00.431 --> 16:03.201
(knocking)
(whispering): Hi.

16:03.236 --> 16:04.268
What are you doing?

16:04.303 --> 16:05.467
